{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0f831306aa","title":"做顶天立地的人","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"92203c1cf8","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"0f831306aa","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"资产阶级反动路线","id":"70f02a0dc7","type":"主题"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"7c9004f11d","name":"清华附中  高六五五班核心组（即领导小组）"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3c6c8fd675","type":"title","text":"做顶天立地的人","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fd6d75edd","type":"paragraph","text":"工农革干子弟们，我们过去受压迫，受排挤，受打击，受尽了凌辱，受尽欺负。现在我们要翻身，要造反，要做主人。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b91f66a20e","type":"paragraph","text":"过去一些工农革干子弟在敌人软硬兼施、名利诱导的情况下，唯唯诺诺、不声不吭，做了一名不闻不问的小人。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c9aac170a5","type":"paragraph","text":"一些工农革干子弟造反未成，灰心丧气，敢怒而不能言。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fcb5c94c46","type":"paragraph","text":"一些工农革干子弟甚至开始蜕化变质，成了敌人的马前卒，牺牲品。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d4ba9eb39a","type":"paragraph","text":"现在，我们要站起来革命了！要造反了！","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e13193d3a7","type":"paragraph","text":"还能再“老实”下去吗？眼看着剥削阶级的孝子贤孙兴风作浪，赤膊上阵，屠杀我们的阶级弟兄却无动于衷？不能！不能！不能！再“沉默”下去，千百万人头落地，大好江山丧失干净！","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd3d97b8be","type":"paragraph","text":"还能再“畏首畏尾以小人自居”吗？让剥削阶级的孝子贤孙趾高气扬、神气十足，当官作老爷，俨然以老子命令威胁我们？不能！不能！不能！再这样下去，剥削阶级的孝子贤孙就会重新夺权，重新掌权，在精神上压倒我们，而我们仍然是敌人精神上的奴隶。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dd417be389","type":"paragraph","text":"不能呀！千万不能再这样下去了！同志们哪，过去我们矮三寸，现在我们要做顶天立地的人！","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"60fd1b7c83","type":"paragraph","text":"班里大权我们掌，核心小组要永远为你们服务！","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45fc043e84","type":"paragraph","text":"我们工农革干子弟要当家做主人，任何出身不好的人在我们面前必须老老实实，不许乱说乱动！","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"708d22b96e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要批判一切旧制度，打击一切反革命，我们要“神气十足”，“作威作福”，要以高姿态出现在高655班。我们要喝斥那些剥削阶级的孝子贤孙，不准翻天，如若乱说乱动，立即镇压！","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4fb725b3b7","type":"paragraph","text":"凡出身非工农革干子弟者，我们可以随意找来谈话。他们在我们面前必须矮三寸！任何非工农革干子弟对我们必须尊重一些，不准恶意中伤！","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e48845f60b","type":"paragraph","text":"我们工农革干子弟还要敢于做工作，和群众紧密结合。谁要有思想问题，我们最有责任去工作！我们要成为高655班的革命先锋，任何革命工作都要成为全班的榜样！","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d147b8eee","type":"paragraph","text":"我们有责任，有权力这样做，因为我们是主人！懂吗？我们是主人！","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0cce50fd2c","type":"paragraph","text":"光荣的，伟大的，自豪的工农革干子弟们，放手干吧！谁敢动工农革干子弟一根毫毛，就砸他个稀巴烂！","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78cfad9599","type":"paragraph","text":"让我们工农革干子弟做主人！","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"06a9afe148","type":"paragraph","text":"红卫兵战校（前清华附中）","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8800afeec5","type":"paragraph","text":"高六五五班核心组（即领导小组）","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"301ab40489","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年八月","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2d9e8551ab","type":"paragraph","text":"（转载于北京：《兵团战报》1966年11月18日）","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"0f831306aa","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}